es today!\n\n**(May only work in the United States due to video hosting issues)**", "short_description": "Prepare your appetite for Cake Player, the only way to view Light Field Layered Depth Light Video -- a layer cake of gooey volumetric goodness that allows for occlusion free 6DoF viewing with some view-dependent effects such as transparency and reflection. Try a slice of the future of movies today!\n\n(May only work in the United States due to video hosting issues)"}]}, "developer_name": "Josh Gladstone", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "http://joshgladstone.com/cake_player_privacy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Josh Gladstone", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://joshgladstone.com/cake_player.html", "category": "ENTERTAINMENT", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2837265163266059", "context_category": "ENTERTAINMENT"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "541611600222565"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["MEDIA_PLAYER"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "595143482567477"}, "review_messages": ["", "", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001679_1858453994602734_4499073466609186507_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=R1Ghgb-t1FoQ7kNvgEwP3bE&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBq3ggvlT4O5qRXAIdNy0sww0kiapn_o9zr-8o2DsoC1Q&oe=66CDAFC9"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "Cake Player: Light Field Video", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "context_category": {"con